    DTDFVocab:producedFrom CranePositionSensor, CraneVelocitySensor, CraneAccelerationSensor, CraneControllerInputSensor, CraneOperationalStatusSensor
    base:desc "Continuously logged state data (position, velocity, acceleration, controller inputs, operational status) transmitted from Physical Crane Interface to TimescaleDB via high-frequency (sub-second/millisecond) updates."
]

